{"tid":746812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp 奪命假消息！Google 工程師慘被村民包圍亂棍打死","createTime":"2018-07-18T01:25:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T02:02:32.000Z","uid":103759,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3cef79d6be5c211b353f3d95eb45091a10ee3746","tid":746812,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T01:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2115000/2117226/images_assettype_com-karnataka_techie_lynched_to_death_over_whatsapp_rumour_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2115000%2F2117226%2Fimages_assettype_com-karnataka_techie_lynched_to_death_over_whatsapp_rumour_1024.jpg&h=1a33e181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前報道過，近年印度 WhatsApp 虛假訊息的問題非常嚴重，日前又再發生慘劇。據外國媒體報道，日前印度一名 Google工程師 Mohammad Azam 與兩名友人，行經 Karnataka 的 Bidar 巿拜訪朋友，途中他的友人派發一些糖果給小孩，卻因村民誤信 WhatsApp 謠言，被當成拐帶兒童的綁匪，最後被村民包圍，慘被亂棍活活打死。<br />\n<br />\n當天 Mohammad Azam 的朋友帶着一些糖果，決定分給該處的小孩，期間一個小孩突然大哭，因之前的 WhatsApp 假消息，附近老人認定他們是拐帶兒童的綁匪。消息瞬間傳遍村落，最後 3 人被 200 多名村民包圍，村民把他們從車上拖出來，並以棍棒及石塊暴打 3 人，期間 3人曾經求饒，但鄉民不予理會。當時村民已經失控，到場的警察亦未能阻止。最後 Mohammad Azam 傷重不治，2 名友人則是重傷送醫，另外還有 3 名警察受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/448FGgTHpMk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F448FGgTHpMk&d=S6G0BtnUd%2F2LN8rd4i%2FdH%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f7a8ea30\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/448FGgTHpMk</a><br />\n<br />\n事後 Mohammad Azam  的兄弟 Akram 十分難過，表示 Mohammad 是一名軟件工程民，只是一個有普通的父親，還有一個 2 歲大的孩子，怎可能是綁匪？至於警方則逮捕了 32 名暴徒，包括一名 Whatsapp 群組管理員，警方認為這個群組的假消息就是害人的源頭。"},{"pid":"861d86ff39746cea018f558e59f3583e33a27c81","tid":746812,"uid":99962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T01:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3287c6eb35c3383d3263d7d312fc281730e1b8","tid":746812,"uid":103759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T01:26:42.000Z","msg":"廢老就真係廢老 究竟可以用幾咁冇知"},{"pid":"f97dc44126b4f674c49b822847c0517c90b7c80f","tid":746812,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T01:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbbb5469a79e14abe01716372b82fe3eb1f03aa5","tid":746812,"uid":61533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T01:27:18.000Z","msg":"印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06ac2aeceb932f656758be0197a578c2e4f584c","tid":746812,"uid":36272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T01:28:47.000Z","msg":"以為發放假消息果個比人打死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9e31d88772abc8f4a08d23c6ec46d70f840eee","tid":746812,"uid":105614,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T01:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 弱智 買起佢成條村屠城啦 以為做錯嘢唔使負責？信錯謠言唔是大晒"},{"pid":"c1f03d91350a01a63fb0e127ab9850d2cf8f225a","tid":746812,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T01:30:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e38f3ca97b586e69e1bd0e91dac41e5a176cfdfb","tid":746812,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T01:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f42994249fd06d0b6f71614eb1155f80f87a4ce","tid":746812,"uid":137966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T01:32:01.000Z","msg":"個小朋友咁就害死左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35664c51cb41494989a65c9f1c262e058b4c425","tid":746812,"uid":13115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T01:32:13.000Z","msg":"蠢人就係地球既毒藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aabf3d1